item.description: Nischal Subedi Data Scientist [ website ] . [ linkedin ] . [ github ] I am a data scientist with a background in credit card and real estate analytics. I have worked on projects that involved researching new algorithms to tackling tough problems, analyzing complex,and poor structured datasets, building novel production ETL and ML infrastructures, and help to bring intelligent capabilities to fruition for users. One of the interesting projects I have worked on recently involved an building infrastructure to constantly monitor micro-markets using live feeds.
